{"tid":271563,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"神奇女俠挑機 雷神認輸","createTime":"2017-06-05T07:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T07:55:19.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"469d70a6674aceeeecd71b694cd4b653575e3df1","tid":271563,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"DC超級英雄電影《神奇女俠》，上映短短幾日，已獲得不少好評，票房成績亦相當理想，預計首個周末會錄得超過1億美元。而身為主角的以色列女星姬嘉鐸，近日繼續四出宣傳，她日前接受訪問時，被問到「如果神奇女俠決戰Marvel的雷神，你認為誰勝誰負？」她笑言：「當然是神奇女俠會贏！基斯(咸斯禾夫)，你認為呢？」基斯得悉被「挑機」後，竟立即認輸，他透過Twitter回應：「我同意神奇女俠會打贏雷神！」姬嘉鐸後來甚至表示：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得可以一試(決鬥)！</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n鬥咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9607b951f56facf0b51861f0540459800a7554a1","tid":271563,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"有crossover，印象中ww同超人都拎起過雷神鎚。"},{"pid":"927b8236540149e066ddf5d1e6b48295192c6f31","tid":271563,"uid":118998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有crossover，印象中ww同超人都拎起過雷神鎚。</blockquote><br />\n其實黑寡婦都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bb2ea9bb7b598cc3c57d45dd2c75059d0e3fd5","tid":271563,"uid":322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有crossover，印象中ww同超人都拎起過雷神鎚。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/155515_cf4c055d9f013e4d13d87885b73a57ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F155515_cf4c055d9f013e4d13d87885b73a57ba.jpg&h=a3c8b63a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/155517_fcc4549df0e5f64560ce7f68d66f1060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F155517_fcc4549df0e5f64560ce7f68d66f1060.jpg&h=16036a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]